Interface ModelDescriber

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AmpApplicationSettingsSerializer, AmpReportColumnSerializer, AmpReportHierarchySerializer, AmpReportMeasureSerializer, AmpTeamSerializer, FilterRuleSerializer, MultilingualContentSerializer

    public interface ModelDescriber
    Use in pair with custom serializers to provider the swagger model. The serializer must also implement this interface in order to describe the model.
